      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong>Â You are the target of a Strike, and you are wielding a melee weapon or Mantle of Deflection</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:.5in\">Using powers of premonition, you raise your weapon or Mantle of Deflection to deflect or otherwise help dodge an incoming attack before it even reaches you. You gain a +2 status bonus to your AC until the end of your next turn. If this would make the attack become a critical miss, you can make a Strike against the target as part of this reaction.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><u>Special</u>: If you use a Mantle of Deflection for this spell, you can choose to turn a critical hit against you into a regular hit. Using the mantle in this way breaks the mantle, causing it to dissipate.</p>"
